{"tid":518070,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(極醜惡Boardgame) 震驚800萬人! 黑警貪污證據確鑿! (2)","createTime":"2018-01-03T03:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T08:17:36.000Z","uid":43487,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"feb4879cc11bddc3b43106504d2e39fd4b62b367","tid":518070,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5s6jmcX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5s6jmcX.jpg&h=3c175291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地講過話整緊隻關於黑警嘅bg (上一個post:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/481214/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/481214/page/1</a>), <br />\n而家我地已經進入最後大直路，預計會喺2月1號放上KICKSTARTER<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地嚟緊呢一個月仲會每個星期都搞多次GIVEAWAY，記住LIKE我地FB，之後嘅GIVEAWAY都會喺個邊搞，上次抽唔中嘅巴絲唔好氣餒，可以再次參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同之前一樣，我地之後如果FUNDED 都會再送出完成品<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有D新圖俾大家睇睇先（未完全FINALIZE）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JUEhoKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJUEhoKS.jpg&h=f879c71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wZs1Y9v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwZs1Y9v.jpg&h=31ec239e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有經過咁多次GAME TEST同大家嘅意見後，遊戲平衡上我地已經改善左唔少，所以之前出嚟試過嘅巴絲有興趣都可以出嚟再試，當然都歡迎之前冇試過嘅巴絲聯絡我地：）<br />\n<br />\n另外，上次抽獎仲有部份巴絲未認領，請盡快聯絡番我地<br />\n<br />\nBomdia #60643<br />\nDMM_AV破解員 #24534<br />\n串過碼頭姑喱 #33673<br />\n切啫琢磨 #52032<br />\n吾你老母咩 #20422<br />\n桂小太郎 #36820<br />\n歷膏 #38044<br />\n殊頭同龜 #7382<br />\n老鼠夾 #20312<br />\n銀灰色的死 #31827<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTG: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/headblownstudio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fheadblownstudio%2F&d=3OAKf2X8IJcTyEPzQ8wmjQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=68ac2aad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/headblownstudio/</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/headblownstudio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fheadblownstudio%2F&d=3OAKf2X8IJcTyEPzQ8wmjQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=385568c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/headblownstudio/</a>"},{"pid":"90176ddd45b687a024657674a586f226d29e2f1a","tid":518070,"uid":43487,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/113414_faaa64fc79cbd3dde7265e2a310b2b1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F113414_faaa64fc79cbd3dde7265e2a310b2b1d.jpg&h=26100e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/113417_85974a71892a355bb8ca956569a3ec3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F113417_85974a71892a355bb8ca956569a3ec3a.jpg&h=f61d73d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少少setup圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff09e8a8528c5d9ea400c25be65ee9ed97b6fa2","tid":518070,"uid":43487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9a7756e8c50299c7ea0baa3b4023509d8e5607","tid":518070,"uid":1391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T07:07:17.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42026c95b544d6ed8a5982151141f3bcc7c8ccf","tid":518070,"uid":17733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"支持本土創作 <img 